translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今のあなたは一人だった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You were alone just now.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたはハニーインザスカイを進むことにした。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You decided to proceed through Hanny in the Sky.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うっはー！　ここが幻の都市、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Whoa! This is the legendary city,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハニーインザスカイかー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hanny in the Sky!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いやさ、いやさ、俺も噂だけは聞いててさ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hey, hey, I’ve only heard rumors too,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いっぺんでいいから来てみたかったんだよねー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I wanted to come here at least once!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 長田君はハニーインザスカイに着いてから
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nagata-kun, after arriving at Hanny in the Sky,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ずっとはしゃいでいた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: had been excited the whole time.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「へへっ、これもお前と冒険続けたからだな！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hehe, this is all because I kept adventuring with you!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サンキューな、＜エール＞！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thanks, <Yell>!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、おいおい！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, hey hey!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 向こうになんか面白そうなもんあるぜ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There’s something interesting over there!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 行ってみようぜ、＜エール＞！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's go check it out, <Yell>!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは長田君に手を引かれながら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You were led by the hand by Nagata-kun

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハニーインザスカイを進んだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: as you progressed through Hanny in the Sky.
"<Yell>, sir……"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……よそ見、危ない」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "…Don’t look away, it’s dangerous."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: キョロキョロと周囲を見回しながら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Looking around restlessly,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 歩いていると、あなたは二人に注意されてしまった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: while walking, you were warned by the two.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大丈夫だと伝えようと、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Trying to tell them you were okay,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後ろ向きに歩いて振り返ると――
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you walked backward and looked back—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＜ズルッ！＞
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: <Slip!>

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「危ない……ッ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Watch out…!"
"...Phew"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 足下を滑らせて転びかけたあなたを、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You almost slipped and fell,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すかさず二人が背を支えてくれた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but the two immediately supported your back.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だ、大丈夫、ですか……？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "A-Are you okay...?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……気を、つけて」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "…Be careful."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは二人に心配されながら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You, worried over by the two,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハニーインザスカイを進む。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: continued through Hanny in the Sky.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はぁ〜……すごいでちね……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Haa~... It's amazing, isn't it..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 松下姫はしばらく歩いても、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Princess Matsushita, even after walking a while,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 初めて見るような景色に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: was captivated by the scenery she seemed to be seeing for the first time.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ポカンと目を奪われていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She was left dumbfounded, her eyes fixed on it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「む、な、なんでち……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "W-why is this...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: わたちのようなレディだって、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even a lady like me,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: わ、ワクワクくらいするものでち」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: can at least get excited."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さ、さあ、行きまちゅわよ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "C-come on, let’s go!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 何故かぷりぷり怒り出した松下姫を追うように、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You chased after Princess Matsushita, who for some reason started pouting angrily,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたはハニーインザスカイを進む。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and continued through Hanny in the Sky.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「アハハハハ、冗談みたいなとこだねー。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ahahaha, this place is like a joke.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私、こういうとこ大好き」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I love places like this."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「私も大概色んなとこ冒険したけど……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I’ve adventured all over the place too, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんなとこが世界にまだ残っていたなんてね……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I never thought a place like this still existed in the world..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「頭痛がしそうな所だわ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "This place feels like it might give me a headache..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ニコニコと楽しそうなナギと対照的に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In contrast to cheerful and happy Nagi,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 志津香は呆れ顔で目をつぶっていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shizuka had an exasperated expression and closed her eyes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こういう所は志津香の趣味ではないらしい。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seemed places like this were not to Shizuka’s taste.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さぁー、ガンガン進んで行こーう♪
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Alright, let’s keep going full speed ahead♪

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ほら、＜エール＞もお姉様も♪」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Come on, <Yell> and big sister too♪"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ、もう、手を引っ張らないの」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, geez, don’t pull my hand so much."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは、はしゃいでいるナギに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You, along with excited Nagi,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 志津香と共に手を引かれ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: were led by the hand together with Shizuka,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハニーインザスカイを進む。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and proceeded through Hanny in the Sky.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はぁーっ、ぽかぽかだねぇー♪」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Haa~ It’s so warm and cozy♪"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットは日向ぼっこ中のにゃんにゃんのように、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset, like a cat sunbathing,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うっとりと目を細めて、太陽の光を全身で浴びる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: narrowed her eyes in bliss, bathing completely in the sunlight.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「えへへ、お弁当作ってきたから、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hehe, I made a packed lunch, so,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You were alone just now.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたはハニーインザスカイを進むことにした。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You decided to proceed through Hanny in the Sky.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Whoa! This is the legendary city,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hehe, this is all because I kept adventuring with you!

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, hey hey!

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There’s something interesting over there!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 行ってみようぜ、＜エール＞！」

"<Yell>, sir……"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……よそ見、危ない」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "…Don’t look away, it’s dangerous."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Looking around restlessly,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: while walking, you were warned by the two.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: <Slip!>

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「危ない……ッ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Watch out…!"
"...Phew"

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but the two immediately supported your back.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……気を、つけて」

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「む、な、なんでち……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "W-why is this...?

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: can at least get excited."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さ、さあ、行きまちゅわよ！」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I love places like this."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I’ve adventured all over the place too, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ、もう、手を引っ張らないの」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You, along with excited Nagi,
